{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block body %}

<div class="card">
	<div class="card-header">
        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
            {{ 'Privacy Policy' }}
        </h5>
	</div>
	<div class="card-body h-100">
        <h2>
            {{ '1. Introduction' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                'Your trust is essential to us. This page explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you interact with our site/application. We are committed to respecting and safeguarding your privacy in accordance with applicable regulations.'
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ '2. Data Collected' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{
                'We only collect the information necessary for the proper execution of our services, including:

                Identification data (name, surname, email address).
                Connection information (IP address, login logs).
                Browsing data (visited pages, user preferences).
                This data is collected with your consent and in compliance with legal obligations.'
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ '3. Use of Data' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                'Your information is used to:

                Provide and personalize our services.
                Ensure the security of our platform.
                Improve your user experience.
                Communicate important updates about our services.
                We will never use your data for unauthorized purposes or without your consent.'
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ '4. Data Security and Protection' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{
                'We take the security of your data very seriously. All personal data you entrust to us is encrypted at every stage of processing, whether in storage or during transmission.

                Encryption: Sensitive data is encrypted using advanced technologies to prevent unauthorized access.
                Restricted Access: Only authorized team members have access to the information necessary for their specific tasks.
                Regular Testing: Our systems are regularly tested to ensure their security.'
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ '5. Data Sharing' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{ 
                'We never share your information with third parties unless necessary to provide our services, comply with legal obligations, or ensure user security.'
            }}
        </p>

        <h2>
            {{ '6. Your Rights' }}
        </h2>
        <p>
            {{
                'In accordance with the law, you have rights over your personal data:

                Access and correction.
                Deletion of your information.
                Opposition to data processing.
                Portability of your data to another platform.
                To exercise your rights, please contact us at [contact email address].'
            }}
        </p>
	</div>
</div>

{% endblock %}

{% block javascripts %}
    {{ parent() }}
    {{ encore_entry_script_tags('settings') }}
{% endblock %}